            <abstract>
                <p>A miniature illustrating <ref type="work" corresp="LIT3589Miracle"/> typically 
                    with as a sequence of three episodes/events, showing: first, the Jewish priest lying on the ground after his fall in the foreground of the miniature; second, 
                    <persName ref="PRS6819Mary"/> sitting on a throne with the two deacons in the background and raising him by her hand;  third, the
                    Jewish priest standing before
                    <persName ref="PRS6819Mary"/>, who is sitting in the same position as in the second episode and performs a <term key="gestureblessing">gesture of blessing</term>.  
                </p>
